Subject: [PATCH] launch-prep round 2: newsletter, verify banner, back-to-top,
 empty state

- Newsletter capture in footer writes to newsletter_subscribers table
- VerifyBanner prompts unverified users to verify email + resend link
- BackToTop floating button appears after 700px scroll
- "No deals match" empty state gains a Clear filters CTA
- User object now carries email_confirmed_at as verified flag
